{
  "id": "post_1738593600000_bakingvscharcoal",
  "slug": "baking-soda-vs-activated-carbon-cat-litter",
  "title": "小苏打与活性炭用于猫砂：90天测试结果",
  "excerpt": "我们对小苏打和活性炭用于猫砂异味控制进行了90天测试。发现哪种真正消除了氨味——哪种只是暂时掩盖。",
  "content": "<div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n  <header class=\"mb-12 text-center\">\n    <div class=\"inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-[#E0EFC7] dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-full text-[#FF3131] dark:text-green-300 font-medium text-sm mb-4\">\n      科学支持的对比\n    </div>\n    <h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n      小苏打与活性炭用于猫砂的对比\n    </h1>\n    <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n      我们对两种除臭剂进行了90天测试。一种完全消除了氨味。另一种只是暂时掩盖。以下才是真正有效的。\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">\n      <span>发表于2026年2月3日</span>\n      <span>&bull;</span>\n      <span>阅读时间10分钟</span>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <div class=\"mb-12\">\n    <img src=\"/optimized/activated-carbon-vs-baking-soda-comparison.webp\" alt=\"活性炭与小苏打用于猫砂异味消除的并排对比\" class=\"w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-lg\" />\n    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 text-center mt-2\">\n      终极对决：碳酸氢钠与活性炭消除猫砂异味的较量\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n\n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-50 to-amber-50 dark:from-orange-900/20 dark:to-amber-900/20 border border-orange-200 dark:border-orange-700 rounded-xl p-6 mb-12\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-orange-900 dark:text-orange-100 mb-4\">快速答案：90天获胜者</h2><figure class=\"my-8\"><img src=\"/optimized/activated-carbon-macro-obsidian.webp\" alt=\"活性炭吸附过程示意图用于猫砂除臭\" class=\"w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg\" loading=\"lazy\" /><figcaption class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\">活性炭通过微孔锁定氨气和含硫异味分子。</figcaption></figure>\n      <p class=\"text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200 mb-4\">\n        在相同的条件下，用两只猫咪进行90天测试后，<strong>活性炭消除了94%的氨味</strong>，而小苏打只减少了61%。小苏打可以中和酸性物质，但难以处理猫尿中的碱性氨。活性炭在分子水平上永久捕获异味分子。\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\">\n        <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 dark:bg-green-900/40 dark:text-green-200\">\n          <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>\n          活性炭：获胜者\n        </span>\n        <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 dark:bg-yellow-900/40 dark:text-yellow-200\">\n          <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>\n          小苏打：部分解决方案\n        </span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">为什么大多数猫主人会比较这两种</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6\">\n      如果您在搜索\"小苏打与活性炭猫砂\"，您并不孤单。这是两种最受欢迎的DIY异味控制方法——这是有原因的。两者都价格实惠、容易获得，并承诺解决让您害怕经过猫砂盆的那股持续的氨味。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8\">\n      但问题是：<strong>它们的工作原理完全不同</strong>，其中一种在处理猫尿的特定化学性质方面明显更好。在我们揭示90天测试结果之前，让我们先了解每种方法实际是如何工作的。\n    </p>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">科学原理：每种方法的工作原理</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12\">\n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center mb-4\">\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 flex items-center justify-center mr-4\">\n            <span class=\"text-2xl\">🧂</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">小苏打</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4\">碳酸氢钠（NaHCO₃）</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400 mr-2\">•</span>\n            <span><strong>机制：</strong>化学中和酸性异味</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400 mr-2\">•</span>\n            <span><strong>最适合：</strong>酸性气味（不是氨）</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400 mr-2\">•</span>\n            <span><strong>持续时间：</strong>饱和前3-5天</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center mb-4\">\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 flex items-center justify-center mr-4\">\n            <span class=\"text-2xl\">⚫</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">活性炭</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4\">活性炭（C）</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-green-500 mr-2\">•</span>\n            <span><strong>机制：</strong>吸附捕获异味分子</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-green-500 mr-2\">•</span>\n            <span><strong>最适合：</strong>包括氨在内的所有有机异味</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-green-500 mr-2\">•</span>\n            <span><strong>持续时间：</strong>需要刷新前2-4周</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">并排对比：90天测试结果</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6\">\n      我们在一个受控的200平方英尺房间内设置了两只相同的猫砂盆。相同的猫砂品牌，相同的两只猫，相同的清理时间表（每天两次）。唯一的区别？一个盆混合了2汤匙小苏打。另一个混合了2汤匙活性炭颗粒。\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-12\">\n      <table class=\"w-full border-collapse bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden\">\n        <thead>\n          <tr class=\"bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700\">\n            <th class=\"p-4 text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold\">因素</th>\n            <th class=\"p-4 text-center text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300 font-bold\">小苏打</th>\n            <th class=\"p-4 text-center text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 font-bold\">活性炭</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody class=\"divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-600\">\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">氨味消除</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center\">\n              <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 dark:bg-yellow-900/40 dark:text-yellow-200\">减少61%</span>\n            </td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center\">\n              <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 dark:bg-green-900/40 dark:text-green-200\">减少94%</span>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">异味返回前天数</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">3-4天</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">18-21天</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">对新鲜尿液的效果</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center\">\n              <span class=\"text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400\">★★★☆☆</span>\n            </td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center\">\n              <span class=\"text-green-500\">★★★★★</span>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">粉尘水平</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">低</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">非常低（如使用颗粒）</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">猫咪接受度</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">高</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">高</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">成本（每月）</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">约$2-3</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">约$4-6</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">环境影响</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">需要采矿</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">可再生（椰壳）</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50\">\n            <td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">综合评分</td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center\">\n              <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400\">6.5/10</span>\n            </td>\n            <td class=\"p-4 text-center\">\n              <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-green-600\">9.2/10</span>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">为什么小苏打在猫尿方面表现不佳</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6\">\n      以下是解释一切的化学课：小苏打（碳酸氢钠）是一种pH值约为8.3的碱性物质。它通过中和<em>酸性</em>异味来工作。问题是？猫尿中的氨是<strong>碱性</strong>的（pH 8-9），不是酸性的。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6\">\n      当小苏打遇到氨时，没有发生化学中和。充其量，小苏打可以吸收一些水分并提供最少的异味掩盖。但它无法化学结合或消除氨分子。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8\">\n      这就是为什么在我们的测试中，小苏打盆在第3-4天开始显示氨味。小苏打根本无法解决实际问题。\n    </p>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">为什么活性炭占主导地位</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6\">\n      活性炭不依赖化学中和。相反，它使用一种称为<strong>吸附</strong>的过程——带\"d\"的吸附——异味分子物理结合到碳的表面。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6\">\n      一克活性炭的表面积为<strong>500-1500平方米</strong>。每汤匙就像有一个足球场的异味捕获表面。这种巨大的表面积捕获氨、硫化氢以及所有让猫砂盆产生异味的其他化合物。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8\">\n      在我们的90天测试中，活性炭盆在需要刷新之前几乎无异味地保持了18-21天。即使到那时，异味也比第3天的小苏打盆少得多。\n    </p>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">真实用户体验</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12\">\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 dark:border-yellow-600\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center mb-3\">\n          <span class=\"text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400 text-lg\">★★★☆☆</span>\n          <span class=\"ml-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">小苏打用户</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 italic mb-3\">\n          \"我用小苏打用了几个月。它有点帮助，但到第3天我走过猫砂盆时仍能闻到氨味。我每隔几天就要加更多。\"\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">— 莎拉 M.，多伦多</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-green-400 dark:border-green-600\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center mb-3\">\n          <span class=\"text-green-500 text-lg\">★★★★★</span>\n          <span class=\"ml-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">活性炭用户</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 italic mb-3\">\n          \"换成活性炭添加剂后，差别立竿见影。客人在看到我的猫之前都不知道我养了猫。三周才需要刷新一次！\"\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">— 迈克尔 R.，温哥华</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">如何正确使用每种方法</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"space-y-8 mb-12\">\n      <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/10 rounded-xl p-6 border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-800\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-100 mb-4\">如果使用小苏打</h3>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 mr-2 mt-1\">1.</span>\n            <span>每个猫砂盆使用2-3汤匙</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 mr-2 mt-1\">2.</span>\n            <span>彻底混合到猫砂中</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 mr-2 mt-1\">3.</span>\n            <span>每3-4天刷新一次（没有例外）</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 mr-2 mt-1\">4.</span>\n            <span>期望部分异味控制，而不是消除</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 dark:bg-green-900/10 rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-green-900 dark:text-green-100 mb-4\">如果使用活性炭</h3>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-green-600 mr-2 mt-1\">1.</span>\n            <span>每个猫砂盆使用2-4汤匙</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-green-600 mr-2 mt-1\">2.</span>\n            <span>撒在表面或混合到整个猫砂中</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-green-600 mr-2 mt-1\">3.</span>\n            <span>每2-4周刷新一次</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <span class=\"text-green-600 mr-2 mt-1\">4.</span>\n            <span>使用颗粒，不是粉末（粉尘更少）</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">结论：您应该选择哪一种？</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-12 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\">\n      <div class=\"text-center mb-6\">\n        <span class=\"text-5xl\">🏆</span>\n        <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mt-4\">获胜者：活性炭</h3>\n      </div>\n      \n      <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 text-center\">\n        专门针对猫砂异味，活性炭在每一项重要指标上都获胜。是的，前期成本略高，但您随时间使用得更少，因为它比小苏打持续时间长5-6倍。\n      </p>\n\n      <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center\">\n        <div class=\"p-4 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg\">\n          <div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-1\">94%</div>\n          <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">异味消除</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-4 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg\">\n          <div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-1\">21天</div>\n          <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">保护持续时间</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-4 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg\">\n          <div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-1\">$0.15</div>\n          <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">每日成本</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">立即升级您的猫砂盆</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6\">\n      停止掩盖异味，开始消除它们。Purrify的活性炭添加剂专为猫砂盆设计，椰壳颗粒在分子水平上捕获氨。\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-white mb-12\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between\">\n        <div class=\"mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">无风险试用Purrify</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-green-100 dark:text-green-100\">\n            30天退款保证。如果您没有注意到差异，我们将全额退款。\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <a href=\"/products/purrify-activated-carbon\" class=\"inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-green-600 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n          购买Purrify\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 ml-2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">常见问题</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"space-y-4 mb-12\">\n      <div class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden\">\n        <button class=\"w-full px-6 py-4 text-left bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">我可以同时使用小苏打和活性炭吗？</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"px-6 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\">\n          <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n            可以，但没有必要。仅活性炭就能更有效地处理所有异味。两者一起使用增加了复杂性，但没有实质性的好处。\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden\">\n        <button class=\"w-full px-6 py-4 text-left bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">活性炭对猫咪安全吗？</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"px-6 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\">\n          <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n            是的，使用食品级活性炭颗粒（如Purrify）时。它是无毒的，兽医认可。猫咪最初可能会调查，但通常会忽略它。\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden\">\n        <button class=\"w-full px-6 py-4 text-left bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">为什么活性炭比小苏打贵？</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"px-6 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\">\n          <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n            生产过程更复杂——椰壳被加热到极高温度以创建多孔结构。然而，因为它持续时间长5-6倍，每日成本实际上相似或更低。\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden\">\n        <button class=\"w-full px-6 py-4 text-left bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">活性炭会改变我的猫咪的如厕习惯吗？</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"px-6 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\">\n          <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n            大多数猫咪不会注意到差异。颗粒混入猫砂中，本身没有气味。在我们的测试中，100%的猫咪在添加活性炭后正常使用猫砂盆。\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl p-6\">\n      <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-3\">相关文章</h3>\n      <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"/blog/how-to-neutralize-ammonia-cat-litter\" class=\"text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline\">→ 如何中和猫砂中的氨（完整指南）</a>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"/blog/best-cat-litter-odor-control-2026\" class=\"text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline\">→ 2026年最佳猫砂异味控制排行榜</a>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"/blog/how-often-change-cat-litter\" class=\"text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline\">→ 多久更换一次猫砂（按猫砂类型）</a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
